CNN - Weed 2 - Cannabis Madness - Dr. Sanjay Gupta reports.

This tv broadcast follows several epilepsy patients, their struggle to find a good medicine and the current state of law about it. Other diseases seems to benefit from cannabis also.
This documentary is a real eyeopener and can convince doctors from everywhere to look for a new cure
